import React, { useState } from 'react'; import axios from "axios"; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; const AddUser = () => { const [Nama_Dokumen, setDokumen] = useState(""); const [Nomor_Surat, setSurat] = useState(""); const [Departement, setDepartement] = useState(""); const [Tanggal_Terbit, setTerbit] = useState(""); const [Tanggal_Exp, setExp] = useState(""); const [Site, setSite] = useState(""); const [Link, setLink] = useState(""); const [Keterangan, setKeterangan] = useState(""); const navigate = useNavigate(); const saveUser = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); try { await axios.post('http://localhost:5001/legal', { Nama_Dokumen, Nomor_Surat, Departement, Tanggal_Terbit, Tanggal_Exp: Tanggal_Exp || null, Site, Link, Keterangan }); navigate("/"); } catch (error) { console.log(error); } } return (
setDokumen(e.target.value)} placeholder='Nama Dokumen' />
setSurat(e.target.value)} placeholder='Nomor Surat' />
setTerbit(e.target.value)} placeholder='Tanggal Terbit' />
setExp(e.target.value)} placeholder='Tanggal Exp' />
setLink(e.target.value)} placeholder='Link' />
setKeterangan(e.target.value)} placeholder='Keterangan' />
) } export default AddUser;
